import React from 'react'
import {Navbar,Container,Nav,FormControl,Form,Button,NavDropdown} from 'react-bootstrap';


 const NavBarLogin = () => {
  return (
    <Navbar className="sticky-top" bg="dark" variant="dark" expand="lg">
      <Container>
        <Navbar.Brand>
        محمد
        </Navbar.Brand>
        <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
        <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
        <Form className="d-flex">
            <Form.Control
              type="بحث"
              placeholder="ابحث"
              className="me-2  w-100 text-center"
              aria-label="Search"
            />
          </Form>
          <Nav className="me-auto">
          <Nav.Link className="nav-text d-flex mt-3 justify-content-cente">More deets</Nav.Link>
          <Nav.Link  href="#memes">
            Dank memes
          </Nav.Link>
        </Nav>
        </Navbar.Collapse>
      </Container>
    </Navbar>

  )
}
export default NavBarLogin;
